{"id": "1181260376990560308", "channel_id": "1181260376990560308", "type": 0, "author_id": "243366124211666944", "author_name": "lai909909911", "author_bot": false, "content": "看了公告今天維修好像沒優化流暢度？試了一下玩起來還是卡卡的.... 會不會是你們遊戲用的字體吃資源比較兇？感覺一次抽到很多牌會卡是文字太多的問題", "timestamp": "2023-12-04T15:47:00.631000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1181260376990560308", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」遊戲優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
